{"type":"message","id":"41b27583","parentId":"f58eb1f1","timestamp":"2026-03-03T23:23:06.649Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了，这个脚本默认回测最近120个交易日（约半年）。我需要修改它来使用2021-2022年的数据。\n\n让我创建一个修改版的回测或者直接修改参数来运行2021-2022年的回测。更好的方式是修改 run_backtest 函数接受参数。\n\n不过，更简单的方法是直接修改代码来选择2021-2022年的数据。让我编辑一下。","thinkingSignature":"25578167db506a0fec4702dc422c034de5f4b60f1d1d6c311bc0d02f9db3711a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zr8okjzkgvuv_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system/backtest.py","newText":"def run_backtest(start_year=2021, end_year=2022):\n    \"\"\"运行回测\n    Args:\n        start_year: 起始年份\n        end_year: 结束年份\n    \"\"\"\n    print(\"📊 小市值策略回测\")\n    print(\"=\" * 50)\n    \n    basic, daily = load_all_data()\n    \n    # 获取所有交易日\n    dates = sorted(daily['trade_date'].unique())\n    print(f\"数据范围: {dates[0]} ~ {dates[-1]}\")\n    print(f\"交易日数: {len(dates)}\")\n    \n    # 选取指定年份的数据\n    recent_dates = [d for d in dates if start_year <= d // 10000 <= end_year]\n    if not recent_dates:\n        # 如果没有指定年份的数据，使用最近120个交易日\n        recent_dates = dates[-120:]\n        print(f\"⚠️ 未找到 {start_year}-{end_year} 年数据，使用最近120个交易日\")\n    \n    start_date = min(recent_dates)\n    end_date = max(recent_dates)\n    \n    print(f\"\\n回测区间: {start_date} ~ {end_date}\")","oldText":"def run_backtest():\n    \"\"\"运行回测\"\"\"\n    print(\"📊 小市值策略回测\")\n    print(\"=\" * 50)\n    \n    basic, daily = load_all_data()\n    \n    # 获取所有交易日\n    dates = sorted(daily['trade_date'].unique())\n    print(f\"数据范围: {dates[0]} ~ {dates[-1]}\")\n    print(f\"交易日数: {len(dates)}\")\n    \n    # 选取最近的时间段回测\n    # 取最近120个交易日\n    recent_dates = dates[-120:]  # 约半年\n    start_date = min(recent_dates)\n    end_date = max(recent_dates)\n    \n    print(f\"\\n回测区间: {start_date} ~ {end_date}\")"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":6208,"output":547,