or?type=mainFloor\n          - img \"头像\" [ref=e24]\n  - main [ref=e25]:\n    - generic [ref=e26]:\n      - generic [ref=e28]:\n        - generic [ref=e30]: 2024国九小市值实盘收益50.64%\n        - generic [ref=e31]:\n          - link \"头像\":\n            - /url: /./user/d4c13f070c69017988b433aa42246a54\n            - img \"头像\" [ref=e33] [cursor=pointer]\n          - generic [ref=e36]:\n            - generic [ref=e37] [cursor=pointer]: zycash\n            - generic [ref=e38]: 1年前 · IP 属地浙江省\n          - generic [ref=e40] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - img [ref=e41]\n            - generic [ref=e43]: 关注\n      - generic [ref=e44]:\n        - generic [ref=e45]:\n          - generic [ref=e46]:\n            - img [ref=e48] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e50]: 点赞 92\n          - generic [ref=e51]:\n            - img [ref=e53] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e55]: \"0\"\n          - generic [ref=e56]:\n            - img [ref=e58] [cursor=pointer]\n            - img [ref=e61] [cursor=pointer]\n            - img [ref=e64] [cursor=pointer]\n            - img [ref=e67] [cursor=pointer]\n        - generic [ref=e69]: 2024国九小市值实盘收益50.64%\n        - generic [ref=e70]:\n          - generic [ref=e72]:\n            - paragraph [ref=e73]:\n              - text: 大家好我是Zycash。之前发过\n              - link \"国九小市值策略【年化100.5%|回撤25.6%】\" [ref=e74] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: https://www.joinquant.com/view/community/detail/f20c03d5ebb66293b870c2eeeea14a02?page=1#398801\n              - text: 这个策略。\n              - text: 我从今年5.1实盘至今，实际收益率位50.64%，于上周五全部清仓，待2025年2月再次入市。今日小盘股全线大跌，主要是受到国九政策落地影响，相信经过1个多月的修复小市值策略会再次崛起。\n              - img \"Img\" [ref=e75]\n            - heading \"从2024.5至2024.12，实际收益率50.64%\" [level=3] [ref=e76]\n            - paragraph [ref=e77]:\n              - img \"Img\" [ref=e78]\n            - heading \"自5月实盘到7月，开始就出现了连续的大幅度回撤，最高22%，后续一路反攻，高歌猛进，如果从最低点到最高点，收益率接近100%\" [level=3] [ref=e79]\n            - paragraph [ref=e80]:\n              - img \"Img\" [ref=e81]\n            - heading \"累计交易25只股票（实际是23只，有两只之前交易的股票），胜率59.09%。\" [level=3] [ref=e82]\n            - paragraph [ref=e83]:\n              - text: 亏损最多的华斯股份002494，主要原因是因为增加了日内两次止损，导致了多次超跌反弹没有吃到，导致了华斯股份的收益率是\n              - strong [ref=e84]: \"-38.58%\"\n              - text: ！！！收益最高的股票是国统股份002205，收益率是\n              - strong [ref=e85]: 43.84%\n              - text: 。如果华斯股份不实行双次止损，实际收益会增高5个点以上。\n              - img \"Img\" [ref=e86]\n            - heading \"我已经于上周五（12-20）全部清仓，只等明年2月再战！\" [level=3] [ref=e87]\n          - generic [ref=e90]:\n            - iframe [ref=e91]:\n              - generic [active] [ref=f17e1]:\n                - generic [ref=f17e5]:\n                  - generic [ref=f17e6]:\n                    - generic [ref=f17e8]: 回测\n                    - list [ref=f17e10]:\n                      - listitem [ref=f17e11]:\n                        - generic [ref=f17e12] [cursor=pointer]: 收益\n                      - listitem [ref=f17e13]:\n                        - generic [ref=f17e14] [cursor=pointer]: 风险\n                      - listitem [ref=f17e15]:\n                        - generic [ref=f17e16] [cursor=pointer]: 源码\n                    - generic [ref=f17e17]:\n                      - generic [ref=f17e18]: Python3\n                      - generic [ref=f17e19]: Code\n                      - generic [ref=f17e22] [cursor=pointer]: 克隆策略\n                      - generic \"该策略已被1885人克隆\" [ref=f17e23]: \"1885\"\n                  - tabpanel [ref=f17e25]:\n                    - generic [ref=f17e26]: 2013-02-01 到 2024-12-16, ￥100000, 每天\n                    - generic [ref=f17e28]:\n                      - generic [ref=f17e29]: 策略收益\n                      - generic [ref=f17e31]: 基准收益\n                    - img [ref=f17e35]:\n                      - generic [ref=f17e37]:\n                        - generic [ref=f17e38]: 缩放：\n                        - generic [ref=f17e41] [cursor=pointer]: 1星期\n                        - generic [ref=f17e44] [cursor