{"type":"message","id":"51d1f955","parentId":"e706dc7f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:21:07.224Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found a great strategy! This is \"2024国九小市值实盘收益50.64%\" by zycash. It has:- Backtest: 2013-02-01 to 2024-12-16- The strategy has made 130000%+ returns (1300x!) over this period- Real trading from May 2024 to December 2024: 50.64% return- Win rate: 59.09%- Maximum drawdown: 22%This is a very good strategy. Let me summarize this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"1cf8ef919275854400fefe9625b13992771fba16c59fe7382db01d11ba12c502"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了一个非常好的策略！\n\n**\"2024国九小市值实盘收益50.64%\"** by zycash\n\n**回测成绩:**\n- 时间：2013-02-01 ~ 2024-12-16\n- **收益：+130000%+** (1300倍!!)\n- 已被 **1885人** 克隆\n\n**实盘成绩:**\n- 2024年5月~12月：+50.64%\n- 胜率：59.09%\n- 持仓25只股票\n\n**策略特点:**\n1. 小市值选股 + 国九条概念\n2. 固定周二调仓\n3. 双重止损机制\n\n这个策略比你的\"简单的策略-35\"(10年595倍) 回测时间更长(11年)，收益更高(1300倍)！\n\n需要我帮你把这个策略克隆到你的账户进行分析和改进吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":106331,"output":307,"cacheRead":18417,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125055,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772587252140}}
