{"type":"message","id":"15a389b3","parentId":"23587e10","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:20:43.909Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"推送成功了！让我告诉用户。","thinkingSignature":"005f12c3b61ea4e3dc726fbb4e3376ab387ea24ff13564dbd21566ad8afeda73"},{"type":"text","text":"已推送到你的 GitHub 仓库！\n\n**仓库地址:** https://github.com/seablue1985/daily_stock_analysis\n\n新增了21个量化策略文件，包括：\n- 回测脚本 (backtest*.py)\n- 数据获取 (fetch_*.py, get_*.py)\n- 策略选股 (selector.py, daily_signal.py)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":126688,"output":84,"cacheRead":18336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145108,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772590838567}}
