{"type":"message","id":"1b965a11","parentId":"55e31e36","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:45:28.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我看看 src/config.py 是怎么配置的。","thinkingSignature":"9cd9be0b6f283bb5f04693974f9a3cd6ff30a77c3224047dd9018076659ec399"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_90r52mdxkfhr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/daily_stock_analysis && head -80 src/config.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":130643,"output":51,"cacheRead":18336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149030,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772592323409}}
{"type":"message","id":"69733492","parentId":"1b965a11","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:45:28.641Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_90r52mdxkfhr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n===================================\nA股自选股智能分析系统 - 配置管理模块\n===================================\n\n职责：\n1. 使用单例模式管理全局配置\n2. 从 .env 文件加载敏感配置\n3. 提供类型安全的配置访问接口\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport re\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import List, Optional, Tuple\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv, dotenv_values\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, field\n\n\ndef setup_env(override: bool = False):\n    \"\"\"\n    Initialize environment variables from .env file.\n\n    Args:\n        override: If True, overwrite existing environment variables with values\n                  from .env file. Set to True when reloading config after updates.\n                  Default is False to preserve behavior on initial load where\n                  system environment variables take precedence.\n    \"\"\"\n    # src/config.py -> src/ -> root\n    env_file = os.getenv(\"ENV_FILE\")\n    if env_file:\n        env_path = Path(env_file)\n    else:\n        env_path = Path(__file__).parent.parent / '.env'\n    load_dotenv(dotenv_path=env_path, override=override)\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass Config:\n    \"\"\"\n    系统配置类 - 单例模式\n    \n    设计说明：\n    - 使用 dataclass 简化配置属性定义\n    - 所有配置项从环境变量读取，支持默认值\n    - 类方法 get_instance() 实现单例访问\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    # === 自选股配置 ===\n    stock_list: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)\n\n    # === 飞书云文档配置 ===\n    feishu_app_id: Optional[str] = None\n    feishu_app_secret: Optional[str] = None\n    feishu_folder_token: Optional[str] = None  # 目标文件夹 Token\n\n    # === 数据源 API Token ===\n    tushare_token: Optional[str] = None\n    \n    # === AI 分析配置 ===\n    # LiteLLM unified model config (provider/model format, e.g. gemini/gemini-2.5-flash)\n    litellm_model: str = \"\"  # Primary model; must include provider prefix when set explicitly\n    litellm_fallback_models: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)  # Cross-model fallback list\n\n    # Multi-key support: each list is parsed from *_API_KEYS (comma-separated) with single-key fallback\n    gemini_api_keys: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)\n    anthropic_api_keys: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)\n    openai_api_keys: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)\n\n    # Legacy single-key fields (kept for backward compatibility; gemini_api_keys[0] when set)\n    gemini_api_key: Optional[str] = None\n    gemini_model: str = \"gemini-3-flash-preview\"  # 主模型\n    gemini_model_fallback: str = \"gemini-2.5-flash\"  # 备选模型\n    gemini_temperature: float = 0.7  # 温度参数（0.0-2.0，控制输出随机性，默认0.7）\n\n    # Gemini API 请求配置（防止 429 限流）\n    gemini_request_delay: float = 2.0  # 请求间隔（秒）\n    gemini_max_retries: int = 5  # 最大重试次数"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":15,"aggregated":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n===================================\nA股自选股智能分析系统 - 配置管理模块\n===================================\n\n职责：\n1. 使用单例模式管理全局配置\n2. 从 .env 文件加载敏感配置\n3. 提供类型安全的配置访问接口\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport re\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import List, Optional, Tuple\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv, dotenv_values\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, field\n\n\ndef setup_env(override: bool = False):\n    \"\"\"\n    Initialize environment variables from .env file.\n\n    Args:\n        override: If True, overwrite existing environment variables with values\n                  from .env file. Set to True when reloading config after updates.\n                  Default is False to preserve behavior on initial load where\n                  system environment variables take precedence.\n    \"\"\"\n    # src/config.py -> src/ -> root\n    env_file = os.getenv(\"ENV_FILE\")\n    if env_file:\n        env_path = Path(env_file)\n    else:\n        env_path = Path(__file__).parent.parent / '.env'\n    load_dotenv(dotenv_path=env_path, override=override)\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass Config:\n    \"\"\"\n    系统配置类 - 单例模式\n    \n    设计说明：\n    - 使用 dataclass 简化配置属性定义\n    - 所有配置项从环境变量读取，支持默认值\n    - 类方法 get_instance() 实现单例访问\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    # === 自选股配置 ===\n    stock_list: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)\n\n    # === 飞书云文档配置 ===\n    feishu_app_id: Optional[str] = None\n    feishu_app_secret: Optional[str] = None\n    feishu_folder_token: Optional[str] = None  # 目标文件夹 Token\n\n    # === 数据源 API Token ===\n    tushare_token: Optional[str] = None\n    \n    # === AI 分析配置 ===\n    # LiteLLM unified model config (provider/model format, e.g. gemini/gemini-2.5-flash)\n    litellm_model: str = \"\"  # Primary model; must include provider prefix when set explicitly\n    litellm_fallback_models: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)  # Cross-model fallback list\n\n    # Multi-key support: each list is parsed from *_API_KEYS (comma-separated) with single-key fallback\n    gemini_api_keys: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)\n    anthropic_api_keys: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)\n    openai_api_keys: List[str] = field(default_factory=list)\n\n    # Legacy single-key fields (kept for backward compatibility; gemini_api_keys[0] when set)\n    gemini_api_key: Optional[str] = None\n    gemini_model: str = \"gemini-3-flash-preview\"  # 主模型\n    gemini_model_fallback: str = \"gemini-2.5-flash\"  # 备选模型\n    gemini_temperature: float = 0.7  # 温度参数（0.0-2.0，控制输出随机性，默认0.7）\n\n    # Gemini API 请求配置（防止 429 限流）\n    gemini_request_delay: float = 2.0  # 请求间隔（秒）\n    gemini_max_retries: int = 5  # 最大重试次数","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772592328633}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf31faf2","parentId":"69733492","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:45:48.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个项目使用 `load_dotenv` 从 `.env` 文件加载配置。它也支持环境变量覆盖。代码显示 `setup_env()` 会加载 `.env` 文件。\n\n用户可以通过以下方式配置：1. 在运行环境中设置环境变量（系统级）2. 在运行命令时设置环境变量\n3. 使用 `.env` 文件（本地开发）\n\n现在让我告诉用户如何在部署时通过环境变量注入。","thinkingSignature":"13b8af3ee1810c1b7e60cf1e00e70b747742f8a604c13fb16072945d186d9a9c"},{"type":"text","text":"有的！这个项目支持环境变量注入。\n\n**方法1：运行命令时设置**\n```bash\nTUSHARE_TOKEN=xxx AIHUBMIX_KEY=xxx MINIMAX_API_KEY=xxx python main.py\n```\n\n**方法2：创建本地 .env 文件（不会被git跟踪）**\n```bash\ncp .env.example .env\n# 然后编辑 .env 填入 token\n```\n\n**方法3：GitHub Actions  secrets（如果你用 CI/CD）**\n- 在 GitHub 仓库 Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions\n- 添加 TUSHARE_TOKEN, AIHUBMIX_KEY, MINIMAX_API_KEY\n- 在 workflow 中用 `${{ secrets.TUSHARE_TOKEN }}` 引用\n\n你想用哪种方式？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":123601,"output":244,"cacheRead":18336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142181,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772592328641}}
{"type":"message","id":"800f26c1","parentId":"bf31faf2","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:45:49.129Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-03-04 10:45 GMT+8] # 克隆自聚宽文章：https://www.joinquant.com/post/66478 # 标题：国证2000 弱转强 # 作者：老爹1231 # -*- coding: utf-8 -*- # 克隆自聚宽文章：https://www.joinquant.com/post/62834 # 标题：国证2000弱转强掘金8支 # 作者：wellfuture # 克隆自聚宽文章：https://www.joinquant.com/post/61567 # 标题：国证2000掘金策略5年140倍年化144% # 作者：空空儿 from jqdata import * import pandas as pd def initialize(context): # 持仓数量 g.stock_num = 8 # 设置策略环境 set_option('use_real_price', True) set_option('avoid_future_data', True) log.set_level('system', 'error') # 设置每日运行计划 run_daily(buy, '09:27') run_daily(buy, '09:27') run_daily(buy, '09:27') run_daily(sell, '11:28') run_daily(sell, '14:50') run_daily(dieting, time=\"every_bar\") run_daily(print_date_separator, time=\"15:05\") # 修正：设置滑点和交易成本 set_slippage(PriceRelatedSlippage(0.0004)) # 修正：添加了缺失的右括号 set_order_cost(OrderCost(open_commission=1/10000, close_tax=5/10000, close_commission=1/10000, min_commission=1), type='stock') # 创建全局变量 g.today_target_list = [] g.dieting_stocks = [] g.max_cash = 80000 def buy(context): \"\"\"买入逻辑：依次执行指数成分筛选、国九条、涨停条件、技术指标、集合竞价、因子排序，最终下单\"\"\" g.dieting_stocks = [] # 第一步：获取指数成分股并过滤ST股 codes = get_index_non_stocks(context) # 第二步：国九条基本面筛选 if codes and is_trade_period(context): codes = filter_by_fundamentals(codes) # 第三步：涨停条件筛选 if codes: codes = filter_by_limit_up(codes, context) # 第四步：技术指标筛选 if codes: codes = filter_by_technical(codes, context) # 第五步：集合竞价筛选 if codes: codes = filter_by_call_auction(codes, context) # 第六步：因子排序 if codes: codes = rank_by_factor(codes, context) # 保存候选股列表用于日志输出 g.today_target_list = codes if codes else [] # 打印候选股信息 hold_list = list(context.portfolio.positions) remaining_positions = g.stock_num - len(hold_list) log.info(f\"今日候选股票数量：{len(g.today_target_list)}只，可买仓位：{remaining_positions}个\") if g.today_target_list: try: display_stocks = g.today_target_list[:10] stock_names = [get_security_info(code).display_name + f\"({code})\" for code in display_stocks] log.info(f\"最终候选股票：{', '.join(stock_names)}\") except: display_stocks = g.today_target_list[:10] log.info(f\"最终候选股票：{', '.join(display_stocks)}\") else: log.info(\"今日无符合条件的候选股票\") # 执行买入操作 if codes: place_buy_orders(codes, context) def sell(context): \"\"\"卖出逻辑：根据7日均线、盈利情况、涨停情况综合判断是否卖出\"\"\" positions = context.portfolio.positions hold_list = list(positions) if not hold_list: return current_data = get_current_data() yesterday = context.previous_date # 历史数据（用于计算均线） hist_data = get_price( hold_list, end_date=yesterday, frequency='daily', fields=['close'], count=8, panel=False ) # 计算7日均线 ma7_data = hist_data.groupby('code')['close'].apply( lambda x: x.rolling(7).mean().iloc[-1] ).to_dict() # 昨日收盘价 df_history = get_price( hold_list, end_date=yesterday, frequency='daily', fields=['close', 'high_limit'], count=1, panel=False ) # 加入持仓与行情数据 df_history['avg_cost'] = [positions[s].avg_cost for s in hold_list] df_history['price'] = [positions[s].price for s in hold_list] df_history['high_limit'] = [current_data[s].high_limit for s in hold_list] df_history['low_limit'] = [current_data[s].low_limit for s in hold_list] df_history['last_price'] = [current_data[s].last_price for s in hold_list] df_history['ma7'] = [ma7_data.get(s, 0) for s in hold_list] df_history['closeable_amount'] = [positions[s].closeable_amount for s in hold_list] # 卖出条件 cond_not_limit_up = (df_history['last_price'] != df_history['high_limit']) cond_break_ma7 = df_history['last_price'] < df_history['ma7'] cond_profit = (df_history['price'] / df_history['avg_cost'] - 1) * 100 > 0 cond_yesterday_limit_up = (df_history['close'] == df_history['high_limit']) sell_condition = cond_not_limit_up & (cond_break_ma7 | cond_profit | cond_yesterday_limit_up) # 最终卖出列表（可卖数量大于0，未跌停） sell_list = df_history[ sell_condition & (df_history['last_price'] > df_history['low_limit']) & (df_history['closeable_amount'] > 0) ].code.tolist() # 执行卖出并记录详细日志 for stock in sell_list: try: position = positions[stock] cost_price = position.avg_cost current_price = current_data[stock].last_price stock_name = get_security_info(stock).display_name # 计算盈亏比例 if cost_price > 0: profit_rate = (current_price / cost_price - 1) * 100 # 判断卖出原因 reason = \"\" if current_price < df_history[df_history['code'] == stock]['ma7'].iloc[0]: reason = \"跌破均线\" elif profit_rate > 0: reason = \"盈利\" else: reason = \"其他\" # 计算卖出金额 sell_amount = position.closeable_amount * current_price log.info(f'🏃 {reason}卖出：{stock_name}({stock}) | 价格：{current_price:.2f}元 | 数量：{position.closeable_amount}股 | 金额：{sell_amount:.0f}元 | 盈亏：{profit_rate:+.2f}%') except: position = positions[stock] current_price = current_data[stock].last_price sell_amount = position.closeable_amount * current_price log.info(f'🏃 卖出：{stock} | 价格：{current_price:.2f}元 | 数量：{position.closeable_amount}股 | 金额：{sell_amount:.0f}元') order_target_value(stock, 0) # ================= 筛选模块 ================= # def get_index_non_stocks(context): # 获取成分股 stocks = get_index_stocks('399303.XSHE', date=context.previous_date) # 过滤ST股 st_flags = get_extras('is_st', stocks, count=1, end_date=context.previous_date).T st_flags.columns = ['is_st'] return st_flags[st_flags['is_st'] == False].index.tolist() def is_trade_period(context): \"\"\"判断当前日期是否在指定交易周期\"\"\" today = context.current_dt.strftime('%m-%d') # 检查是否在1、4、12月的特定交易周期内 return ( '01-15' <= today <= '01-31' or '04-15' <= today <= '04-30' or '12-15' <= today <= '12-31' ) def filter_by_fundamentals(stocks): \"\"\"国九条：过滤净利润/ROE/ROA/营收等不达标的股票\"\"\" # 构建财务数据查询 q = query( valuation.code, income.np_parent_company_owners, income.net_profit, income.operating_revenue, indicator.roe, indicator.roa ).filter( valuation.code.in_(stocks), income.np_parent_company_owners > 0, income.net_profit > 0, income.operating_revenue > 1e8, indicator.roe > 0, indicator.roa > 0 ) # 获取并返回符合条件的股票 df = get_fundamentals(q) return list(df.code) def filter_by_limit_up(stocks, context): \"\"\"筛选昨日未涨停且前日涨停的股票\"\"\" # 获取股票过去两天的收盘价和涨停价 prices = get_price( stocks, end_date=context.previous_date, frequency='daily', fields=['close', 'high_limit'], count=2, panel=False ).reset_index() # 重构数据结构 prices['day_rank'] = prices.groupby('code').cumcount() pivot = prices.pivot(index='code', columns='day_rank', values=['close', 'high_limit']) pivot.columns = ['close_day_before', 'close_yesterday', 'hl_day_before', 'hl_yesterday'] # 筛选条件：昨日未涨停且前日涨停 cond = (pivot['close_yesterday'] < pivot['hl_yesterday']) & \\ (pivot['close_day_before'] == pivot['hl_day_before']) result = pivot[cond].index.tolist() return result def filter_by_technical(stocks, context): \"\"\"技术面筛选：均线、成交量、价格条件\"\"\" # 获取历史数据用于技术指标计算 hist = get_price( stocks, end_date=context.previous_date, fields=['close', 'low', 'volume'], count=11, panel=False ).reset_index() # 计算技术指标 hist['ma10'] = hist.groupby('code')['close'].transform(lambda x: x.rolling(10).mean()) hist['prev_low'] = hist.groupby('code')['low'].shift(1) hist['prev_volume'] = hist.groupby('code')['volume'].shift(1) # 获取最新一天的数据 last_data = hist.groupby('code').tail(1) # 技术面筛选条件 cond = ( (last_data['close'] > last_data['prev_low']) & (last_data['close'] > last_data['ma10']) & (last_data['volume'] > last_data['prev_volume']) & (last_data['volume'] < 10 * last_data['prev_volume']) & (last_data['close'] > 1) ) result = last_data.loc[cond, 'code'].tolist() return result def filter_by_call_auction(stocks, context): \"\"\"集合竞价筛选\"\"\" date_now = context.current_dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\") start, end = date_now + ' 09:15:00', date_now + ' 09:26:00' auction = get_call_auction( stocks, start_date=start, end_date=end, fields=['time','a1_p','a1_v','a2_p','a2_v','a3_p','a3_v','a4_p','a4_v','a5_p','a5_v', 'b1_p','b1_v','b2_p','b2_v','b3_p','b3_v','b4_p','b4_v','b5_p','b5_v','current'] ).reset_index() # 检查数据是否为空 if auction is None or auction.empty: return [] # 获取昨收数据 pre_close = get_price( stocks, end_date=context.previous_date, fields=['close'], count=1, panel=False ).reset_index() auction = auction.merge(pre_close[['code', 'close']], on='code', how='left') auction = auction.rename(columns={'close': 'pre_close'}) # 计算买卖盘金额 auction = auction.assign( sellmoney=lambda df: df['a1_p'] * df['a1_v'] + df['a2_p'] * df['a2_v'] + df['a3_p'] * df['a3_v'] + df['a4_p'] * df['a4_v'] + df['a5_p'] * df['a5_v'], buymoney=lambda df: df['b1_p'] * df['b1_v'] + df['b2_p'] * df['b2_v'] + df['b3_p'] * df['b3_v'] + df['b4_p'] * df['b4_v'] + df['b5_p'] * df['b5_v'] ) # 计算买盘与卖盘的差值比率 auction['b_s'] = (auction['buymoney'] - auction['sellmoney']) / auction['sellmoney'] # 筛选买盘大于卖盘且价格在合理区间的股票 result = auction.query( 'b_s > 0 and current > 0.95*pre_close and current < 1.01*pre_close' )['code'].tolist() return result def rank_by_factor(stocks, context): \"\"\"因子排序：换手率 × (竞价价/昨收)，返回所有符合条件的股票\"\"\" # 获取换手率（上一交易日数据） val = get_valuation( stocks, end_date=context.previous_date, fields=['turnover_ratio'], count=1 ).reset_index() # 获取集合竞价数据（取当天09:15-09:26的最后一笔作为开盘） date_now = context.current_dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\") start, end = date_now + ' 09:15:00', date_now + ' 09:26:00' auction = get_call_auction( stocks, start_date=start, end_date=end, fields=['time', 'current'] ).reset_index() # 取每只股票最后一条竞价作为开盘价 auction = auction.sort_values(['code', 'time']).groupby('code').tail(1) auction.rename(columns={'current': 'open'}, inplace=True) # 获取昨收 pre_close = get_price( stocks, end_date=context.previous_date, fields=['close'], count=1, panel=False ).reset_index() pre_close.rename(columns={'close': 'pre_close'}, inplace=True) # 合并数据 df = pd.merge(val[['code', 'turnover_ratio']], auction[['code', 'open']], on='code', how='inner') df = pd.merge(df, pre_close[['code', 'pre_close']], on='code', how='inner') # 计算因子：换手率 × (竞价价/昨收) df['factor'] = df['turnover_ratio'] * (df['open'] / df['pre_close']) # 排序返回所有股票 result = df.sort_values(by='factor', ascending=False)['code'].tolist() return result def place_buy_orders(stocks, context): # 获取当前持仓和可买数量 hold_list = list(context.portfolio.positions) num = g.stock_num - len(hold_list) if num <= 0: return # 筛选不在持仓中的股票 stocks = [s for s in stocks if s not in hold_list][:num] if not stocks: return # 修正：计算每只股票的买入金额 cash_per_stock = min(context.portfolio.available_cash / len(stocks), g.max_cash) current_data = get_current_data() for stock in stocks: # 检查股票状态：是否停牌、是否涨停、是否跌停 if (current_data[stock].paused or current_data[stock].last_price in [current_data[stock].low_limit, current_data[stock].high_limit]): continue # 获取股票名称 try: stock_name = get_security_info(stock).display_name except: stock_name = stock # 计算买入金额 price = current_data[stock].last_price amount = int(cash_per_stock / price / 100) * 100 # 向下取整到100的倍数 # 检查是否有足够的资金 min_cost = price * 100 if cash_per_stock < min_cost: log.info(f'跳过买入：{stock_name}({stock}) | 原因：资金不足，最低需要{min_cost:.2f}元') continue order_amount = amount * price # 执行买入操作并记录日志 order(stock, amount) log.info(f'👉️ 买入：{stock_name}({stock}) | 价格：{price:.2f}元 | 数量：{amount}股 | 金额：{order_amount:.0f}元') def dieting(context): \"\"\"监控跌停票\"\"\" current_data = get_current_data() # 检查持仓股是否跌停 for s in list(context.portfolio.positions): if s not in g.dieting_stocks: dtj = current_data[s].low_limit zxj = current_data[s].last_price if zxj == dtj and (context.portfolio.positions[s].closeable_amount != 0): if s not in g.dieting_stocks: g.dieting_stocks.append(s) g.dieting_stocks = list(set(g.dieting_stocks)) # 检查跌停股是否打开 if len(g.dieting_stocks) > 0: for s in g.dieting_stocks[:]: dtj = current_data[s].low_limit zxj = current_data[s].last_price if zxj > dtj: try: stock_name = get_security_info(s).display_name position = context.portfolio.positions[s] cost_price = position.avg_cost current_price = current_data[s].last_price # 计算盈亏比例 if cost_price > 0: profit_rate = (current_price / cost_price - 1) * 100 # 计算卖出金额 sell_amount = position.closeable_amount * current_price log.info(f\"🏃 跌停打开止损卖出：{stock_name}({s}) | 价格：{current_price:.2f}元 | 数量：{position.closeable_amount}股 | 金额：{sell_amount:.0f}元 | 盈亏：{profit_rate:+.2f}%\") except: current_price = current_data[s].last_price sell_amount = position.closeable_amount * current_price log.info(f\"🏃 跌停打开止损卖出：{s} | 价格：{current_price:.2f}元 | 数量：{position.closeable_amount}股 | 金额：{sell_amount:.0f}元\") order_target_value(s, 0) g.dieting_stocks.remove(s) def print_date_separator(context): \"\"\"收盘后打印日期分隔线\"\"\" log.info(\"=\" * 60) 学习一下这个弱转强的策略"}],"timestamp":1772592349125}}
{"type":"message","id":"955925bb","parentId":"800f26c1","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:46:12.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我学习一下这个弱转强策略。这是一个聚宽上的量化策略，名为\"国证2000弱转强\"，主要逻辑是：\n\n1. 持仓数量：8只\n2. 买入逻辑：\n   - 获取指数成分股（国证2000 399303）\n   - 过滤ST股\n   - 国九条基本面筛选（净利润>0, ROE>0, ROA>0, 营收>1亿）\n   - 涨停条件筛选（昨日未涨停且前日涨停）\n   - 技术指标筛选（均线、成交量）\n   - 集合竞价筛选\n   - 因子排序（换手率 × 竞价价/昨收）\n\n3. 卖出逻辑：\n   - 跌破7日均线\n   - 盈利\n   - 昨日涨停\n\n4. 风控：\n   - 跌停止损\n   - 1/4/12月空仓期\n\n让我给用户总结一下这个策略的核心逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"583a538dfac86acb0b6cd2cf7fcd4b69edc776a942e8c93ad854eb852f929aef"},{"type":"text","text":"这是一个非常好的弱转强策略！让我总结一下核心逻辑：\n\n## 国证2000弱转强策略\n\n**📊 策略参数**\n- 持仓：8只\n- 选股池：国证2000成分股 (399303)\n- 空仓期：1月、4月、12月\n\n**🛒 买入逻辑（6步筛选）**\n1. **指数成分** → 获取国证2000成分股，过滤ST\n2. **国九条** → 净利润>0, ROE>0, ROA>0, 营收>1亿\n3. **涨停条件** → 昨日未涨停 且 前日涨停\n4. **技术面** → 收盘>10日均线 且 放量突破\n5. **集合竞价** → 买盘>卖盘，价格在-5%~+1%\n6. **因子排序** → 换手率 × (竞价价/昨收)\n\n**🏃 卖出逻辑**\n- 跌破7日均线 → 卖出\n- 盈利 → 卖出\n- 昨日涨停 → 卖出\n- 跌停打开 → 止损\n\n---\n\n这个策略比之前的国九策略更复杂，加入了：\n- 弱转强形态（前日涨停昨日未涨停）\n- 集合竞价筛选\n- 因子排序\n\n需要我把这个策略实现到本地回测系统吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":497,"cacheRead":18336,"cacheWrite":127561,"totalTokens":146430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772592349128}}
