{"type":"message","id":"91b28ebf","parentId":"91cc0331","timestamp":"2026-03-04T04:02:49.919Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-04 11:59:37 GMT+8] Exec completed (tidy-hav, code 0) :: ture: Screen recorder fabric-app: Personal knowledge management and note-taking app font-gmarket-sans vcmi: Open-source engine for Heroes of Might & Magic III You have 2 outdated …\nSystem: [2026-03-04 12:02:49 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM from ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080: 介绍discord\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-04 12:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b554ea05fc0a8c2e4a5149f1ae1a]\n张玲: 介绍discord"}],"timestamp":1772596969914}}
{"type":"message","id":"673af17b","parentId":"91b28ebf","timestamp":"2026-03-04T04:03:08.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想了解Discord。让我简单介绍一下。","thinkingSignature":"ec0cbf31d5ae4ce6fbca2348c62b3953ac1e5b8922f1f4f039ded37c3a874c85"},{"type":"text","text":"**Discord** 是一款免费的即时通讯应用，主要特点：\n\n**功能：**\n- **语音/视频通话** - 支持群组语音频道\n- **文字聊天** - 支持服务器、频道、私信\n- **屏幕共享** - 适合远程协作/游戏\n- **机器人集成** - 可自动执行任务、发送通知\n\n**使用场景：**\n- 游戏社区\n- 开发团队协作\n- 学习群组\n- OpenClaw 也可以通过 Discord 接收通知\n\n**你已经安装好了**，可以：\n1. 打开 Discord 应用\n2. 登录账号（或注册新账号）\n3. 加入服务器（如 OpenClaw 的服务）\n\n需要我帮你在 OpenClaw 中配置 Discord 通知吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":162,"cacheRead":159653,"cacheWrite":820,"totalTokens":160671,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772596969917}}
{"type":"message","id":"b67ba1cd","parentId":"673af17b","timestamp":"2026-03-04T04:09:58.135Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-04 12:09:57 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM from ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080: discord跟飞书的区别？优劣势\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-04 12:09 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b554f479f98a0c2d3e0c7444405f]\n张玲: discord跟飞书的区别？优劣势"}],"timestamp":1772597398129}}
{"type":"message","id":"a3b6b761","parentId":"b67ba1cd","timestamp":"2026-03-04T04:10:08.175Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想了解Discord和飞书的区别和优劣势。","thinkingSignature":"345f0a57e926905618498e2bade613721bd51acf494e639cab6132ca8e161c65"},{"type":"text","text":"**Discord vs 飞书对比**\n\n| 方面 | Discord | 飞书 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| **定位** | 社区/游戏聊天 | 企业协作办公 |\n| **体验** | 简洁、免费 | 功能多、适合办公 |\n| **机器人** | 强大丰富 | 基础配置 |\n| **文件** | 有限制 | 无限云文档 |\n| **语音** | 免费高质量 | 企业版才免费 |\n| **国内** | 需要VPN | 纯国内 |\n| **生态** | 开发者友好 | 字节生态 |\n\n**推荐：**\n- **个人/开源项目** → Discord（免费、机器人强大）\n- **企业协作** → 飞书（文档、审批一体化）\n- **你的场景** → 飞书更适合（已在用），Discord 可作为补充\n\n你平时用飞书主要是做什么？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":197,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":160758,"totalTokens":160991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772597398133}}
