{"type":"message","id":"648a888b","parentId":"3f535e5a","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:38:31.308Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从截图中可以看到用户的健身计划：\n\n2026年2月健身记录\n\n第4周 02.24-02.28（周一～周五）\n- 周一：胸\n- 周二：背+三头\n- 周三：肩+有氧\n- 周四：臀+有氧\n- 周五：二头+三头+有氧\n\n周末休息\n\n这是2月份的健身计划，是按部位分化的练法。让我更新健身提醒cron任务，使用正确的计划。","thinkingSignature":"7d60c522d3a190bf3e0a1eb7bf28b5e50e2facbfe8f3d93ef88f2608011ddfbf"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！这是你2月份的健身计划：\n\n**周一：胸**\n**周二：背+三头**\n**周三：肩+有氧**\n**周四：臀+有氧**\n**周五：二头+三头+有氧**\n**周末：休息**\n\n让我更新健身提醒：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yo6gjzy3joi9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\njobs = json.load(sys.stdin)\nfor job in jobs['jobs']:\n    if '健身' in job['name']:\n        # 更新为正确的消息\n        job['payload']['message'] = '''发送当天健身计划:\n周一：胸\n周二：背+三头\n周三：肩+有氧\n周四：臀+有氧\n周五：二头+三头+有氧\n周末：休息'''\nprint(json.dumps(jobs, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n\" > /tmp/jobs_new.json && mv /tmp/jobs_new.json ~/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":134914,"output":334,"cacheRead":18417,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153665,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772602685900}}
