{"type":"message","id":"96da60a9","parentId":"f24974b3","timestamp":"2026-03-04T10:15:23.684Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll create the SKILL.md file for this new skill.","thinkingSignature":"51bcd804975a75f96bed47bc0157a9a648d9a1a7c2a69ea8c9c4656b1bc4b5e8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_td4at2d5bdat_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: web-scraper\ndescription: |\n  网页转Markdown工具。当需要从URL获取内容并转换为Markdown格式时使用此技能。\n  适用场景：(1) 获取网页文章内容 (2) 提取网页数据 (3) 将HTML转为Markdown\n  方法优先级：1) markdown.new  2) r.jina.ai  3) defuddle.md  4) Scrapling爬虫\n---\n\n# 网页转 Markdown\n\n当需要从URL获取内容时，按以下优先级尝试：\n\n## 方法1: markdown.new（推荐）\n\n在URL前添加 `https://markdown.new/`\n\n```\nhttps://markdown.new/https://example.com\n```\n\n## 方法2: r.jina.ai\n\n使用 Jina AI 读取器\n\n```\nhttps://r.jina.ai/https://example.com\n```\n\n## 方法3: defuddle.md\n\n```\nhttps://defuddle.md/https://example.com\n```\n\n## 方法4: Scrapling（备选爬虫）\n\n如果以上方法都失败，使用 Scrapling：\n\n```bash\npip install scrapling\nscrapling https://example.com --markdown\n```\n\n或用 Python:\n\n```bash\npip install scrapling\npython -c \"from scrapling import Fetcher; print(Fetcher().get('https://example.com').markdown())\"\n```\n\n## 使用示例\n\n获取网页内容：\n1. 先尝试 `https://r.jina.ai/{url}`\n2. 如果失败，尝试 `https://markdown.new/{url}`\n3. 如果都失败，使用 Scrapling\n\n获取标题、摘要、正文等结构化内容用 r.jina.ai 效果最好。\n","file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/web-scraper/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":121462,"output":398,"cacheRead":19905,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141765,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772619309979}}
