{"type":"message","id":"1518d92d","parentId":"f936e79a","timestamp":"2026-03-04T10:15:49.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"r.jina.ai works perfectly! The skill is created and tested. Let me tell the user.","thinkingSignature":"050fd16bbe4814d00ae47b4a87dbce30fe86deb4eeb593ef84390eb5bf603eb7"},{"type":"text","text":"**web-scraper** 技能已创建并测试成功！\n\n**使用方法：**\n- 当需要获取网页内容时，我会自动使用 `r.jina.ai/{url}` 转换\n\n**测试成功：** 获取了 Hacker News 页面内容\n\n现在可以让我帮你搜信息了！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117425,"output":82,"cacheRead":19905,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137412,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772619329734}}
