{"type":"message","id":"4cf5c961","parentId":"4eb671ab","timestamp":"2026-03-04T10:18:50.565Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"技能创建好了。让我告诉用户。","thinkingSignature":"d09cc5ad0ea737bd95dc8c289f32d0e85c74c9013733d966acb786c5d8b9d57f"},{"type":"text","text":"**joinquant-strategy** 技能已创建！\n\n**功能：**\n1. 🔍 搜索聚宽优秀策略\n2. 📊 分析回测指标（年化、夏普、回撤）\n3. 📋 提取策略逻辑\n4. 🛠️ 改进策略（止损、仓位、空仓月）\n\n**已实现的改进方法：**\n- 添加-10%止损\n- 调整持仓数量和仓位\n- 过滤ST股\n- 空仓月（1、4、12月）\n\n现在可以帮你找聚宽策略了！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":118034,"output":129,"cacheRead":19905,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138068,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772619523014}}
