{"type":"message","id":"ac23718e","parentId":"497bc7f3","timestamp":"2026-03-04T10:24:29.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"登录成功了！我看到用户的聚宽主页，显示了一些策略和精选策略。\n\n社区精选中看到了一些热门策略：\n1. 年化64%的市值选股策略（有止损模块）- 3822人\n2. 年化42%的市值选股与阶梯调仓策略 - 3822人\n\n让我去社区搜索更多高收益策略。","thinkingSignature":"7b9386b72eac1a59656f9543768b239b62a1ca0aa04b12746f6353e8a18bf64f"},{"type":"text","text":"登录成功！看到你的聚宽主页。\n\n**发现的热门策略：**\n\n| 策略 | 年化收益 | 热度 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 年化64%市值选股（有止损） | 64% | 3822人 |\n| 年化42%阶梯调仓策略 | 42% | 3822人 |\n| 多因子策略入门 | 199% | 52115人 |\n| 股指期货跨期套利 | 56% | 16823人 |\n\n让我去社区找更多高收益策略：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zq46igwexpup_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","profile":"openclaw","targetUrl":"https://www.joinquant.com/community/new"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":132455,"output":242,"cacheRead":19905,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152602,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772619854119}}
