{"type":"compaction","id":"0c1d104d","parentId":"01895323","timestamp":"2026-03-04T11:02:53.133Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Download stock data (2021-2024 years) and run backtests\n2. Optimize small-cap stock strategy with stop-loss, position management, and risk control\n3. Access user's JoinQuant account to find and learn from successful public strategies\n4. Configure OpenClaw to use MiniMax model (switching from Gemini)\n5. Set up GitHub repository (forked ZhuLinsen/daily_stock_analysis to seablue1985/daily_stock_analysis)\n6. Analyze stock 利通电子 (603629.SH) - K-line + sector/fundamentals\n7. Improve OCR capabilities\n8. Create web-scraper skill and JoinQuant strategy discovery skill\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- MiniMax token: sk-cp-TypyXejs2B15_iA2InVLaRhZBTL_wxRXO5ut0AXIl6elvqblH6fWp3j8VaUulYChdYV6fEHnXtMyNwRhaeHBmxI_dFoOwRlmtPdSZt6pwrMvqKU92zBfir8\n- AIHUBMIX token: sk-B2eHf2gNLcrUeyZZA7D0F25c20354aCaB57fC4A9A6684c14\n- Tushare token: fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc\n- JoinQuant credentials: 337968914@qq.com / sea1985823, logged in as username: 旺旺旺23 (phone: 13890002221)\n- User wants comprehensive stock analysis combining K-line + sector/fundamentals\n- Fitness schedule: Mon (chest), Tue (back+triceps), Wed (shoulders+cardio), Thu (glutes+cardio), Fri (biceps+triceps+cardio), Weekend (rest)\n\n## Progress\n\n### Done\n- [x] Downloaded 2021-2024 stock data to ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system/data/\n- [x] Ran original small-cap strategy backtest (2021-2024): Total return +107.39%, Annual 20.47%, Max drawdown -49.87%\n- [x] Created optimized version with 10% stop-loss in backtest_v4.py\n- [x] Optimized results: Total return +541.29%, Annual 60.72%, Max drawdown -18.86%, Sharpe 1.88\n- [x] Successfully logged into JoinQuant account\n- [x] Found \"2024国九小市值实盘收益50.64%\" strategy by zycash (130000%+ return over 11 years, cloned 1885 times)\n- [x] Ran local version of Guojiu strategy: Total return +128.24%, Annual 6.34%, Max drawdown -29.82%\n- [x] Successfully obtained Tushare financial data: 16,700 records for 167 stocks (fields: ts_code, end_date, roe, eps)\n- [x] Added MINIMAX_API_KEY and AIHUBMIX_API_KEY to OpenClaw config\n- [x] Forked ZhuLinsen/daily_stock_analysis to seablue1985/daily_stock_analysis\n- [x] Cloned repo to ~/.openclaw/workspace/daily_stock_analysis\n- [x] Created backtest_guojiu_v2.py with 国九小市值策略 optimization\n- [x] Backtest results (optimized): 总收益 +131.32%, 年化31.11%, 夏普0.90, 最大回撤-28.58%, 胜率55.9%\n- [x] Installed Discord via Homebrew\n- [x] Installed Tesseract OCR + Chinese language pack\n- [x] Created web-scraper skill at ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/web-scraper/SKILL.md\n- [x] Created joinquant-strategy skill at ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/joinquant-strategy/SKILL.md\n- [x] Corrected stock code: 利通电子 is 603629.SH (not 603129)\n- [x] Calculated loss for 603629.SH: -9.1% (cost 63元, current 57.24元 from Tonghuashun)\n- [x] Pushed code to GitHub\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Switching Gemini to MiniMax model in GitHub-deployed project\n\n### Blocked\n- [x] Tushare IP limit issue - resolved after waiting\n- [x] AKShare and yfinance network issues - resolved with Tushare\n- [x] Wrong stock code 603129 - resolved, correct is 603629.SH\n- [ ] Xiaohongshu access - domain blocked due to security compromise (451 security error)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Added 10% stop-loss**: Changed strategy from losing 50% in drawdown to 18.86%, while increasing annual return from 20% to 60%\n- **Used PE>0 as proxy for net profit>0** when financial data unavailable\n- **Used Tushare for financial data** after AKShare and yfinance failed\n- **Corrected stock code**: User's stock is actually 603629.SH (利通电子), not 603129 as initially assumed\n- **Used r.jina.ai for web scraping**: Web-scraper skill uses this as primary method to convert URLs to markdown\n- **Strategy selection**: Chose 国九小市值策略 (by zycash) for backtesting as it has verified live trading results (50.64% return in 2024)\n- **Local backtest vs platform**: Implemented strategy locally using available data instead of cloning directly from JoinQuant\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Complete switching to MiniMax model in user's GitHub project\n2. Integrate Tushare financial data (roe, eps) into backtest strategy\n3. Run backtest with financial filtering (ROE > 0 or net profit > 0)\n4. Wait for Xiaohongshu access to be restored or ask user to register an account\n5. Continue optimizing 国九小市值策略 with more improvements\n6. Try other high-return strategies found on JoinQuant\n\n## Critical Context\n- Data directory: ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system/data/\n- Main backtest file: ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system/backtest_v4.py\n- Financial data: ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system/data/financial_tushare.csv (16,700 records)\n- JoinQuant logged in as: 13890002221 (username: 旺旺旺23)\n- Stock position: 利通电子 (603629.SH) - cost 63元, current 57.24元 (from Tonghuashun), loss ~9.1%\n- Repo: https://github.com/seablue1985/daily_stock_analysis\n- Skills created:\n  - web-scraper: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/web-scraper/\n  - joinquant-strategy: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/joinquant-strategy/\n- Fitness schedule saved to: ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-04.md\n- MiniMax token: sk-cp-TypyXejs2B15_iA2InVLaRhZBTL_wxRXO5ut0AXIl6elvqblH6fWp3j8VaUulYChdYV6fEHnXtMyNwRhaeHBmxI_dFoOwRlmtPdSZt6pwrMvqKU92zBfir8\n- Tushare token: fa7fe5039b58853bd0df3fc31f1770fc4a8cfaa79c6bff0473829bbc\n- AIHUBMIX token: sk-B2eHf2gNLcrUeyZZA7D0F25c20354aCaB57fC4A9A6684c14\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n- View a specific quantitative trading strategy on JoinQuant (聚宽) platform titled \"经过7次优化的1进2策略\" (1进2 strategy optimized 7 times)\n- The user provided account credentials for access\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- User explicitly stated: \"给了你账号密码，自己去看\" (gave you account credentials, go check yourself)\n- Assistant should browse the JoinQuant platform to find and view the strategy details\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Navigated to