_commission=0, min_commission=0), type='stock') log.set_level('order', 'error') log.set_level('system', 'error') g.no_trading_today_signal = False g.run_stoploss = True g.hold_list = []\"\n  - textbox [ref=e24] [nth=1]: 2019-01-01 00:00:00\n  - text: 至\n  - textbox [ref=e25] [nth=2]: 2025-12-31 23:59:59\n  - text: ￥\n  - textbox [ref=e26] [nth=3]: \"1000000\"\n  - button \"每天\" [ref=e27]\n  - combobox [ref=e28]:\n    - option \"Python3\" [ref=e29] [selected]\n    - option \"Python2 (已下线)\" [ref=e30] [disabled]\n  - text: 运行回测 策略收益 -- 基准收益 -- Alpha -- Beta -- Sharpe -- 最大回撤  -- 点击”编译运行\"进行快速回测(Ctrl-Alt-B) 或者 点击\"运行回测\"进行详细的回测\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"日志\" [ref=e31]:\n        - /url: \"#daily-logs-tab\"\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"错误\" [ref=e32]:\n        - /url: \"#daily-errors-tab\"\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"50b8da41d0d9404e\">>>"}],"details":{"ok":true,"format":"ai","targetId":"AE3D527A09173AD1BC4B8B3AC11D2F4D","url":"https://www.joinquant.com/algorithm/index/edit?algorithmId=3eef106bad355eb00711b438dfe50401","stats":{"lines":70,"chars":3727,"refs":32,"interactive":31},"refs":32,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"browser","kind":"snapshot","format":"ai","wrapped":true}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772622399315}}
