{"type":"message","id":"7baefad6","parentId":"78c484e0","timestamp":"2026-03-04T13:11:54.677Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The simplified version is much faster and shows good results:\n\n- Total return: 54.94%\n- Annual return: 16.39%\n- Max drawdown: -12.36%\n- Sharpe: 2.24\n\nThis is much better risk-adjusted returns! The simplified version with basic filtering (price 3-50, ROE>0) and simple rebalancing every 5 days gives good results with much lower drawdown.\n\nLet me report this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"3263580b9da9d0275fbc6548b8e3a191c5abfd696a4e840a8212b05af840a7c8"},{"type":"text","text":"**策略91简化版回测成功！**\n\n| 指标 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| 初始资金 | 1,000,000 |\n| 最终价值 | 1,549,421 |\n| **总收益** | **54.94%** |\n| **年化** | **16.39%** |\n| **最大回撤** | **-12.36%** |\n| **夏普** | **2.24** |\n\n**对比：**\n- 简化版（本地）：年化16.39%，回撤12.36%，夏普2.24 ✅\n- 原版（聚宽）：年化更高，但需要更多数据\n\n**核心逻辑：**\n- 股价3-50元\n- ROE>0（财务过滤）\n- 市值排序选小盘\n- 止损10%，止盈35%\n- 每5天轮动\n\n这个版本回撤控制得很好（12.36%），夏普高达2.24！要保存这个策略吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":99414,"output":317,"cacheRead":19956,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119687,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772629905835}}
