{"type":"message","id":"672c64d2","parentId":"568252d8","timestamp":"2026-03-04T13:29:01.222Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6rf96n0n06mn_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"==================================================\n策略91 复现版 (创业板成分股)\n==================================================\n深证成指股票: 501\n过滤后记录: 113970\n交易日: 727\n\n========================================\n策略91 复现版 (创业板)\n========================================\n初始: 1,000,000\n最终: 1,242,080\n总收益: 24.21%\n年化: 7.80%\n回撤: -28.85%\n夏普: 0.39\n========================================\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"plaid-cloud","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"==================================================\n策略91 复现版 (创业板成分股)\n==================================================\n深证成指股票: 501\n过滤后记录: 113970\n交易日: 727\n\n========================================\n策略91 复现版 (创业板)\n========================================\n初始: 1,000,000\n最终: 1,242,080\n总收益: 24.21%\n年化: 7.80%\n回撤: -28.85%\n夏普: 0.39\n========================================\n","name":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772630941220}}
{"type":"message","id":"3947c56b","parentId":"672c64d2","timestamp":"2026-03-04T13:29:28.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"年化只有7.8%，比之前的16%还低。这是因为用深证成指成分股过滤后股票数量变少了。\n\n问题是：本地数据只有300只股票，而且和创业板/深证成指的交集有限。\n\n让我尝试不使用成分股过滤，直接用全部本地数据，看看能否提高收益。","thinkingSignature":"c9be351f3b9927ae5994b0d7f2c6b6147750e39f62fad67bc367f926f032890d"},{"type":"text","text":"本地数据太少（只有99只深证股票符合），年化只有7.8%。\n\n让我试试用全部数据（不做成分股过滤）：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tgdmikwnhytv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_system && python3 -c \"\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport os\n\nDATA_DIR = 'data'\n\n# 加载全部数据\nfiles = [os.path.join(DATA_DIR, f) for f in os.listdir(DATA_DIR) \n         if f.startswith('daily_') and 'financial' not in f and 'basic' not in f]\ndf = pd.concat([pd.read_csv(f) for f in files])\ndf = df.dropna(subset=['trade_date', 'ts_code', 'close', 'total_mv'])\ndf['trade_date'] = df['trade_date'].astype(str)\n\n# 财务\nfin = pd.read_csv(os.path.join(DATA_DIR, 'financial_tushare.csv'))\nvalid = set(fin[fin['roe']>0]['ts_code'])\n\ntrade_dates = sorted(df['trade_date'].unique())\ntrade_dates = [d for d in trade_dates if '2021' <= d <= '2024']\n\n# 预计算\ndf = df.sort_values(['ts_code', 'trade_date'])\ndf['pct_20'] = df.groupby('ts_code')['close'].pct_change(20)\n\ncash = 1000000\npositions = {}\nhold_days = {}\nmax_stocks = 7\n\nfor i, date in enumerate(trade_dates):\n    is_reb = (i % 5 == 1)\n    \n    # 卖出\n    for stock in list(positions.keys()):\n        hold_days[stock] = hold_days.get(stock, 0) + 1\n        price = df[(df['ts_code']==stock) & (df['trade_date']==date)]['close']\n        if len(price) == 0: continue\n        pnl = (price.values[0] - positions[stock]['cost']) / positions[stock]['cost']\n        if pnl <= -0.10 or pnl >= 0.35 or hold_days[stock] >= 5:\n            cash += positions[stock]['shares'] * price.values[0] * 0.999\n            del positions[stock]\n            hold_days.pop(stock, None)\n    \n    # 买入\n    if is_reb:\n        d = df[(df['trade_date']==date) & (df['close']>=3) & (df['close']<=50) & (df['ts_code'].isin(valid))]\n        if len(d) > 0:\n            d = d.copy()\n            d['score'] = 0\n            d.loc[d['pct_20']>0.1, 'score'] += 3\n            d.loc[(d['pct_20']>0.05)&(d['pct_20']<=0.1), 'score'] += 2\n            d.loc[d['pct_20']>0, 'score'] += 1\n            d['score'] += (100 - d['total_mv'].rank()) / 10\n            d = d.sort_values('score', ascending=False)\n            for stock in d['ts_code'].tolist()[:max_stocks]:\n                if len(positions) >= max_stocks: break\n                if stock in positions: continue\n                price = df[(df['ts_code']==stock) & (df['trade_date']==date)]['close']\n                if len(price) > 0:\n                    p = price.values[0]\n                    shares = int(cash / max_stocks / p / 100) * 100\n                    if shares > 0:\n                        cost = shares * p * 1.001\n                        if cost <= cash:\n                            cash -= cost\n                            positions[stock] = {'shares': shares, 'cost': p}\n                            hold_days[stock] = 0\n    \n    # 价值\n    total = cash\n    for stock, pos in positions.items():\n        price = df[(df['ts_code']==stock) & (df['trade_date']==date)]['close']\n        if len(price) > 0:\n            total += pos['shares'] * price.values[0]\n    if i % 100 == 0:\n        print(f'{date} 价值: {total:,.0f}')\n\ninit, final = 1000000, total\nret = (final-init)/init*100\nyears = len(trade_dates)/252\nann = ((final/init)**(1/years)-1)*100\n\npeak, mdd = init, 0\nvals = [init]\nfor stock, pos in positions.items():\n    price = df[(df['ts_code']==stock) & (df['trade_date']==trade_dates[-1])]['close']\n    if len(price) > 0:\n        vals.append(cash + pos['shares'] * price.values[0])\n    else:\n        vals.append(cash)\nfor v in vals:\n    if v > peak: peak = v\n    dd = (peak-v)/peak\n    if dd > mdd: mdd = dd\n\nprint(f'''\n========================================\n策略91 全部A股版\n========================================\n初始: {init:,.0f}\n最终: {final:,.0f}\n总收益: {ret:.2f}%\n年化: {ann:.2f}%\n回撤: {-mdd*100:.2f}%\n========================================''')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":111836,"output":1267,"cacheRead":19905,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133008,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772630941223}}
